text: Nur () is a rural locality (a village) in Kandrinsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 31 as of 2010. There is 1 street.Карта Туймазинского района Башкортостана == Geography == It is located 25 km from Tuymazy, 14 km from Kandry. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Nur, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
